{"tid":304301,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩好食嘅雪條介紹","createTime":"2017-06-30T18:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T17:53:00.000Z","uid":10292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46d992433f677e590f8e5891ebbddc4489d95c7c","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:47:39.000Z","msg":"最鍾意嗰隻雀巢橙味同檸檬味雪條冇得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我可以一日砌四支橙味四支檸檬味<br />\n屌佢老味"},{"pid":"efb0f6dbe0f189c353c24f1cbbcf8e5812432d4e","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"食完支棍中獎拎多條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c6d01d368f77d1924ef9cea26d3eee76df10b8","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"冇人食雪條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f47c6babf6993903cb19554eea31f2a0dde184","tid":304301,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:56:40.000Z","msg":"閣下係咪為食肥妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1179713fb8095653af44a7c335d0c6821e030348","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閣下係咪為食肥妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為食大隻佬"},{"pid":"790fedc254bb1fe31a2b2a13ae7b6cf48a24dc24","tid":304301,"uid":12823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://iphoto.ipeen.com.tw/photo/comment/8/5/9/cm20120714_36708_108859_0f6440b6fb5524129ebc87428e181bf4989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiphoto.ipeen.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcomment%2F8%2F5%2F9%2Fcm20120714_36708_108859_0f6440b6fb5524129ebc87428e181bf4989.jpg&h=486b88ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有奶有豆有冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c945d488e98f6f6aee5f65372ac6c5b8d732ab","tid":304301,"uid":39971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:03:12.000Z","msg":"阿菠蘿雪糕雪條大部份都又平又好味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nok 7-11最近啲韓國雪條好撚on9 尤其係水果味嗰啲 廿蚊條但味道好一般<br />\nok之前有個脆皮咖啡雪條好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ded5648b6ab1715af0c855dd72d3c3344bf7b8b","tid":304301,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿菠蘿雪糕雪條大部份都又平又好味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nok 7-11最近啲韓國雪條好撚on9 尤其係水果味嗰啲 廿蚊條但味道好一般<br />\nok之前有個脆皮咖啡雪條好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個益力多雪條<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2b342b382c732513b9df77accd3e94e7cc4134","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿菠蘿雪糕雪條大部份都又平又好味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nok 7-11最近啲韓國雪條好撚on9 尤其係水果味嗰啲 廿蚊條但味道好一般<br />\nok之前有個脆皮咖啡雪條好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n韓國雪糕之前有隻芝士蛋糕味同芒果味唔錯<br />\n阿波羅我幾鍾意佢個雪糕沙冰定唔知乜鳩"},{"pid":"58eedeb99a641761516217f442cb218f0d318de1","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://iphoto.ipeen.com.tw/photo/comment/8/5/9/cm2