芝士雪條好好食<br />\n仲有出糯米滋<br />\n<br />\n好似跌撚左入忌廉芝士嘅陷阱裏面咁"},{"pid":"c9e8f39e7c11929b82dc57debb183dca7ac3ed6d","tid":304301,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>豆豆樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個有食 覺得綠豆味麻麻</blockquote><br />\n紅豆味好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過依家貴咗好多"},{"pid":"d77f71f525eb5dc7d9e32719d87e8a5c834d325d","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>豆豆樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個有食 覺得綠豆味麻麻</blockquote><br />\n紅豆味好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過依家貴咗好多</blockquote><br />\n好撚香甜"},{"pid":"0f41495215f87238fcba3392a92da031af6444c3","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:13:21.000Z","msg":"笨nana都好食<br />\n仲有出爆炸糖版<br />\n<br />\n個重點係塊啫哩皮"},{"pid":"c721fd56ac1534619ec8f1105b4c5672310e4398","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:20:53.000Z","msg":"毒撚輕推"},{"pid":"5eac10f9bc16f7b92357b477d23da8879f90fb5c","tid":304301,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://iphoto.ipeen.com.tw/photo/comment/8/5/9/cm20120714_36708_108859_0f6440b6fb5524129ebc87428e181bf4989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiphoto.ipeen.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcomment%2F8%2F5%2F9%2Fcm20120714_36708_108859_0f6440b6fb5524129ebc87428e181bf4989.jpg&h=486b88ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有奶有豆有冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有奶通常唔錯 已mark低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我食綠色宇治金時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae298f25154feeb402d997eeb35e351664523e0","tid":304301,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"華潤有得賣"},{"pid":"e09c57d14228b4c5cfb96be4ccd33f81d5e1b8bd","tid":304301,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:11:29.000Z","msg":"以前有隻雪條明治出既好似十角 不過好耐唔見有"},{"pid":"0d922698536bcde36a5f59176b4bac84ba81c5ea","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華潤有得賣</blockquote><br />\n而家都好少見到華潤"},{"pid":"a596f5236cb9bf4012683f27fe0171053822183b","tid":304301,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2v60wCFISV4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2v60wCFISV4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fc695f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/d0039085_1204768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fd0039085_1204768.jpg&h=f6257409&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"738e74e93ac6b512f7849fbf81996df38636557a","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2v60wCFISV4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2v60wCFISV4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fc695f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/d0039085_1204768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fd0039085_1204768.jpg&h=f6257409&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪有隻係朱古力奶味<br />\n<br />\n細個成日食"},{"pid":"099d613c633322c5e8e97214549a683993cb2543","tid":304301,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2v60wCFISV4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2v60wCFISV4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fc695f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/d0039085_1204768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fd0039085_1204768.jpg&h=f6257409&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n童年回憶嘅雪條口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上圖係牛奶公司(現雀巢雪糕)，左起朱古力脆皮，鳳仙，古力樂，牛奶樂，旺寶，紅豆，綠豆<br />\n下圖係早已停產嘅嘉頓雪條，聽講好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6166a9ff8d24e67ae3890a12a2d1bdf59d65c3","tid":304301,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"來自:&nbsp;香港網絡大典&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n雪條潮文<br />\n<br />\n内容列表<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n警告：條目可能具有冒犯性、恐怖、淫褻、粗言穢語或其他未成年人不良的內容。使用或閱讀本條目可能違反當地的法律，詳情請參看香港網絡大典:內容聲明，並自行考慮應否閱讀這些內容。<br />\nWarning: Some coarse language(s),offensive and obscene content(s) may included in this article. Using or reading this article may violate the law of the location. ReadEVCHK:Statement of Contents&nbsp;(Chinese only) for more information and consider whether you should read this article.<br />\n<br />\n係我7歲果年買左一枝雪條，從此改變我既一生<br />\n當我奶到最後一啖好失落時，<br />\n枝棍竟然仲多兩條，唔洗講即刻去換黎食<br />\n<br />\n我食完第二枝，吊，又中兩條；<br />\n而第三枝，又仲兩條！結果我再去換四條番黎<br />\n當我食完第五枝後，唔洗講，又中兩條，<br />\n但我已食唔落了，果次係我人生第一次食唔落雪條<br />\n<br />\n我拎番第6~8枝番去比屋企人食，果然每枝再分別各中兩條<br />\n如是者我已經可以再換16條番黎，人生果然充滿希望<br />\n但當我拎番去比屋企人食完後，呢16枝又再各中兩枝，<br />\n我手上渣住16條可兌換32枝既雪條棍，我開始感到到d驚<br />\n<br />\n今次我換完拎番去比同學食，中伏！！<br />\n每枝又獎多兩枝，即係64枝，<br />\n點算？我已幾乎請過晒我識既人食雪條了！<br />\n於是我請埋隔黎班食，但冇喇冇喇，再獎128枝，<br />\n7歲既我，要一次過拎128枝雪條係何其吃力<br />\n<br />\n就咁樣捱左半年，<br />\n我手上仲有20736枝可換41472枝雪條既雪條棍，<br />\n我快要崩潰了！<br />\n難道我餘下既半生都只能活係雪條中嗎！？<br />\n<br />\n轉眼到我24歲果年，<br />\n我已類積左3487459498594498枝一兌二既雪條棍，<br />\n為左搵地方擺雪條，<br />\n我將同女友同居新買既家私全部當晒，<br />\n再用錢去買雪櫃黎裝，<br />\n然後每個月女友一出糧就叫佢比晒錢我買雪櫃去裝，<br />\n但真係冇辦法!!<br />\n我搵錢買雪櫃既速度遠遠追唔上食雪條中雪條既速度!!!!<br />\n<br />\n終於，係我26歲生日果日，女友離我而去，<br />\n佢一句話都冇同我講，<br />\n因為佢個咀已食雪條食到硬化唔講得野。<br />\n我好對佢唔住，<br />\n但人生...我又可以點？<br />\n<br />\n呢年我全個家族因為不停買雪櫃而破產，<br />\n我家族本來係中古時期既貴族後裔，<br />\nd錢洗十世都用唔晒，但竟然落得如廝田地，<br />\n而且我仲有8千幾兆既雪條未換。<br />\n部分擺唔入雪櫃既雪條開始溶化，<br />\nd雪水浸到上我心口，<br />\n我好凍，凍到失去知覺...<br />\n就咁樣一訓，唔知訓左幾多年。<br />\n<br />\n我醒番時掰大眼見到個呀伯，佢話有辦法幫我，<br />\n我問點樣，佢就話只要將我手上既雪條棍賣晒比佢，<br />\n佢就會開一間雪條公司賣雪條，<br />\n等人買左後再拎雪條棍黎換，<br />\n<br />\n比如10個人買左10條，<br />\n走番黎獎20條，佢就前後清左30條；<br />\n果廿條再獎四十條，佢再比，又清多八十條...<br />\n如是者向全世界輻射出去，最終就會解脫到<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，一路多謝佢一路&rarr;即走，<br />\n走左成百米遠後我回頭問佢係咩人，<br />\n佢答我係瑞士人，叫亨利內斯特萊。<br />\n<br />\n雀巢公司，就係佢成立。"},{"pid":"174675746fbd4c3e6e4eb732f3c8a6cdd64a4cf5","tid":304301,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>華潤有得賣</blockquote><br />\n而家都好少見到華潤</blockquote><br />\n頭先行咗去<br />\n原來唔係冰冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係旺寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8506d409edae22bc42461db927137a889a68cc50","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2v60wCFISV4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2v60wCFISV4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fc695f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/d0039085_1204768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fd0039085_1204768.jpg&h=f6257409&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n童年回憶嘅雪條口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上圖係牛奶公司(現雀巢雪糕)，左起朱古力脆皮，鳳仙，古力樂，牛奶樂，旺寶，紅豆，綠豆<br />\n下圖係早已停產嘅嘉頓雪條，聽講好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家啲小學生應該感受唔到一日啪幾支平雪條嘅快感"},{"pid":"5b5f08674003347d753e8789a468e483ca171f58","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>華潤有得賣</blockquote><br />\n而家都好少見到華潤</blockquote><br />\n頭先行咗去<br />\n原來唔係冰冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係旺寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚彩我冇突登去搵<br />\nBtw<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebd6aacbab70606708361d42139e37dcdcba94c","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>來自:&amp;nbsp;香港網絡大典&amp;nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n雪條潮文<br />\n<br />\n内容列表<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n警告：條目可能具有冒犯性、恐怖、淫褻、粗言穢語或其他未成年人不良的內容。使用或閱讀本條目可能違反當地的法律，詳情請參看香港網絡大典:內容聲明，並自行考慮應否閱讀這些內容。<br />\nWarning: Some coarse language(s),offensive and obscene content(s) may included in this article. Using or reading this article may violate the law of the location. ReadEVCHK:Statement of Contents&amp;nbsp;(Chinese only) for more information and consider whether you should read this article.<br />\n<br />\n係我7歲果年買左一枝雪條，從此改變我既一生<br />\n當我奶到最後一啖好失落時，<br />\n枝棍竟然仲多兩條，唔洗講即刻去換黎食<br />\n<br />\n我食完第二枝，吊，又中兩條；<br />\n而第三枝，又仲兩條！結果我再去換四條番黎<br />\n當我食完第五枝後，唔洗講，又中兩條，<br />\n但我已食唔落了，果次係我人生第一次食唔落雪條<br />\n<br />\n我拎番第6~8枝番去比屋企人食，果然每枝再分別各中兩條<br />\n如是者我已經可以再換16條番黎，人生果然充滿希望<br />\n但當我拎番去比屋企人食完後，呢16枝又再各中兩枝，<br />\n我手上渣住16條可兌換32枝既雪條棍，我開始感到到d驚<br />\n<br />\n今次我換完拎番去比同學食，中伏！！<br />\n每枝又獎多兩枝，即係64枝，<br />\n點算？我已幾乎請過晒我識既人食雪條了！<br />\n於是我請埋隔黎班食，但冇喇冇喇，再獎128枝，<br />\n7歲既我，要一次過拎128枝雪條係何其吃力<br />\n<br />\n就咁樣捱左半年，<br />\n我手上仲有20736枝可換41472枝雪條既雪條棍，<br />\n我快要崩潰了！<br />\n難道我餘下既半生都只能活係雪條中嗎！？<br />\n<br />\n轉眼到我24歲果年，<br />\n我已類積左3487459498594498枝一兌二既雪條棍，<br />\n為左搵地方擺雪條，<br />\n我將同女友同居新買既家私全部當晒，<br />\n再用錢去買雪櫃黎裝，<br />\n然後每個月女友一出糧就叫佢比晒錢我買雪櫃去裝，<br />\n但真係冇辦法!!<br />\n我搵錢買雪櫃既速度遠遠追唔上食雪條中雪條既速度!!!!<br />\n<br />\n終於，係我26歲生日果日，女友離我而去，<br />\n佢一句話都冇同我講，<br />\n因為佢個咀已食雪條食到硬化唔講得野。<br />\n我好對佢唔住，<br />\n但人生...我又可以點？<br />\n<br />\n呢年我全個家族因為不停買雪櫃而破產，<br />\n我家族本來係中古時期既貴族後裔，<br />\nd錢洗十世都用唔晒，但竟然落得如廝田地，<br />\n而且我仲有8千幾兆既雪條未換。<br />\n部分擺唔入雪櫃既雪條開始溶化，<br />\nd雪水浸到上我心口，<br />\n我好凍，凍到失去知覺...<br />\n就咁樣一訓，唔知訓左幾多年。<br />\n<br />\n我醒番時掰大眼見到個呀伯，佢話有辦法幫我，<br />\n我問點樣，佢就話只要將我手上既雪條棍賣晒比佢，<br />\n佢就會開一間雪條公司賣雪條，<br />\n等人買左後再拎雪條棍黎換，<br />\n<br />\n比如10個人買左10條，<br />\n走番黎獎20條，佢就前後清左30條；<br />\n果廿條再獎四十條，佢再比，又清多八十條...<br />\n如是者向全世界輻射出去，最終就會解脫到<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，一路多謝佢一路&rarr;即走，<br />\n走左成百米遠後我回頭問佢係咩人，<br />\n佢答我係瑞士人，叫亨利內斯特萊。<br />\n<br />\n雀巢公司，就係佢成立。</blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb5652801f5ad87120435e5976a9faa6fbcb237","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"雪糕都可以講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e3f3b4b77caf416fc368234547d09a45fdacf2","tid":304301,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2v60wCFISV4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2v60wCFISV4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fc695f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/d0039085_1204768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fd0039085_1204768.jpg&h=f6257409&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n童年回憶嘅雪條口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上圖係牛奶公司(現雀巢雪糕)，左起朱古力脆皮，鳳仙，古力樂，牛奶樂，旺寶，紅豆，綠豆<br />\n下圖係早已停產嘅嘉頓雪條，聽講好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家啲小學生應該感受唔到一日啪幾支平雪條嘅快感</blockquote><br />\n而家啲平雪條好似冇晒散裝賣咁，得番家庭裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲小朋友一食就已經係哈根大師，縱壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前有零用錢只會買到牛奶公司雪條、汽水、維他奶咁<br />\nDreyers、哈根大師呢啲係屬於大人嘅食物"},{"pid":"f12c25f91676ea4dcd8914190b502511f1ac8315","tid":304301,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2v60wCFISV4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2v60wCFISV4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fc695f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/d0039085_1204768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fd0039085_1204768.jpg&h=f6257409&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n童年回憶嘅雪條口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上圖係牛奶公司(現雀巢雪糕)，左起朱古力脆皮，鳳仙，古力樂，牛奶樂，旺寶，紅豆，綠豆<br />\n下圖係早已停產嘅嘉頓雪條，聽講好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家啲小學生應該感受唔到一日啪幾支平雪條嘅快感</blockquote><br />\n而家啲平雪條好似冇晒散裝賣咁，得番家庭裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲小朋友一食就已經係哈根大師，縱壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前有零用錢只會買到牛奶公司雪條、汽水、維他奶咁<br />\nDreyers、哈根大師呢啲係屬於大人嘅食物</blockquote><br />\n時代嘅眼淚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca08165498ec60e60bd288a0dbc8d72ff42c318","tid":304301,"uid":2720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"能得利荔枝/提子雪條 <br 