 />\n部分擺唔入雪櫃既雪條開始溶化，<br />\nd雪水浸到上我心口，<br />\n我好凍，凍到失去知覺...<br />\n就咁樣一訓，唔知訓左幾多年。<br />\n<br />\n我醒番時掰大眼見到個呀伯，佢話有辦法幫我，<br />\n我問點樣，佢就話只要將我手上既雪條棍賣晒比佢，<br />\n佢就會開一間雪條公司賣雪條，<br />\n等人買左後再拎雪條棍黎換，<br />\n<br />\n比如10個人買左10條，<br />\n走番黎獎20條，佢就前後清左30條；<br />\n果廿條再獎四十條，佢再比，又清多八十條...<br />\n如是者向全世界輻射出去，最終就會解脫到<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，一路多謝佢一路&rarr;即走，<br />\n走左成百米遠後我回頭問佢係咩人，<br />\n佢答我係瑞士人，叫亨利內斯特萊。<br />\n<br />\n雀巢公司，就係佢成立。</blockquote><br />\n邊間公司有咁多雪條比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec62f1a143f9c21f8672d548ea4f250752514c5","tid":304301,"uid":67657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>秦式雪條都好味<br />\n有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img0.etsystatic.com/064/0/9659882/il_570xN.758777046_n672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg0.etsystatic.com%2F064%2F0%2F9659882%2Fil_570xN.758777046_n672.jpg&h=ee3c8699&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度有賣</blockquote><br />\n次次去翟都翟市集都啪幾支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6a9e35ae47d66d9879f97a4fc2011a6e252613","tid":304301,"uid":25649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>牛牛雪條，\b$3一支好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知正確名係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學小食部有<br />\n朱古力味，食緊好似含撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>